&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen within the Occupational Therapy team based at the Hartington Unit in Chesterfield for a Band 6 Senior Occupational Therapist.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a new, dynamic, forward-thinking team; always striving to obtain innovated ways of working.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking to recruit an experienced, enthusiastic and motivated Band 6 Occupational Therapist, who has an interest in providing care to adults with mental health issues within an acute inpatient setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be responsible for leading and supporting the Ward Based Occupational Therapists across the Unit to develop and provide an effective Occupational Therapy service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;April Saunders, Clinical Advanced Lead Occupational Therapist Manager, at april.saunders@nhs.net or on 07917 506475.&lt;/p&gt;
